### 🎤 Voice-Controlled Dashboard Demo  

This demo showcases a voice-controlled dashboard interface built using Fast Whisper and Python. The system processes voice commands and dynamically updates a simulated vehicle control dashboard, including engine status, wipers, headlights, and indicators.

▶ [Watch Voice-Controlled Dashboard Demo](https://youtu.be/VKOTKlumzl4)  

The video demonstrates real-time voice command recognition, UI responsiveness, and seamless interaction between speech input and dashboard state changes within a simulated environment.
